{"tid":984542,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【驚睇唔明】英大學涉歧視華學生 警告勿cheating加註中文「舞弊」","createTime":"2019-01-17T01:37:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T06:37:41.000Z","uid":224561,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3e40df99dd9b08ef363e34950c859c9886570c06","tid":984542,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T01:37:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190116/59148299\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190116%2F59148299&d=ENjt5TdXBxjpftf5WjULUI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=faa26b06\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190116%2F59148299&h=387ac3b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190116/59148299</a><br />\n<br />\n英文電郵附加一個敏感詞的中文字解釋，算不算歧視？英國利物浦大學（University of Liverpool）近日向外國留學生發送了一封電郵，提醒他們在考試期間作弊的嚴重後果，卻因在英文字cheating後特別用中文「舞弊」作註解，令來自中國的學生十分不滿。<br />\n<br />\n有中國留學生向校方表達不滿，認為有關做法具爭議。<span style=\"color: red;\">校方隨後回覆指，這是因為「學校的中國學生通常不熟悉cheating這一英文單詞，所以我們提供了它的中文繙譯『舞弊』」。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n這個解釋令在該校就讀的中國留學生更加不滿，他們認為校方不該在發給所有國際學生的英文郵件中，單獨使用中文解釋敏感詞彙，此舉明顯涉嫌歧視，會讓人覺得來自中國的學生都有作弊的可能。<br />\n<br />\n校方後來又發聲明，就事件所引發的誤解致歉之餘，還表示之前發出有關考試的提醒，並非針對某特定學生群體。不過，校方仍堅持，因為以往出現過中國學生對英文不理解，加上中文繙譯只是為了更好地傳達考試規範。<br />\n<br />\n內地網友對今次事件反應兩極，有網友認為，「應該自省自律，反思中國留學生到底是否存在作弊較為嚴重的情況。感覺涉嫌歧視，還是談不上。」但亦有人指，「哪個留學生會連『Cheating』是甚麼意思都不知道？未免太針對中國人了」、「我看是中國學生成績太好你們懷疑是『舞弊』來的，分明是嫉妒！」 ​<br />\n<br />\n《中國日報》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190116/large/1547603281_af4d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190116%2Flarge%2F1547603281_af4d.jpg&h=d25b7544&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國利物浦大學發電郵，被指歧視中國學生。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190116/large/1547603281_1ef4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190116%2Flarge%2F1547603281_1ef4.jpg&h=48508955&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電郵在cheating後特別用中文「舞弊」作註解。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190116/large/1547603281_7b94.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190116%2Flarge%2F1547603281_7b94.jpg&h=efd2d6c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n校方隨後回覆，作出解釋。(互聯網)"},{"pid":"2be85249fe19469525f04cd8ef759cf808ff714a","tid":984542,"uid":136186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T01:40:27.000Z","msg":"寸過馬撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69d992646f4e2d1e85489decbc36ebef0a5947c2","tid":984542,"uid":90259,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T01:40:54.000Z","msg":"不嬲去英國留學嘅唔少支那官富二代係唔識英文<br />\n用中文注明先係符合蟈情<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4083f0c0bdceda89dee1dc008380a71049eda632","tid":984542,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T01:41:42.000Z","msg":"坦白講唔識英文出國留學不如返屋企含撚"},{"pid":"ff5546207e58b3aa65a5b17697779a958038d346","tid":984542,"uid":29211,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T01:44:56.000Z","msg":"坦白講 身邊有一半中國留學生係完全唔講英文"},{"pid":"e83cd397ec85ddbfa4a881b3aae6c7f8251d69b1","tid":984542,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff5546207e58b3aa65a5b17697779a958038d346","tid":984542,"uid":29211,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T01:44:56.000Z","msg":"坦白講 身邊有一半中國留學生係完全唔講英文"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T01:47:48.000Z","msg":"但大學都收？咁間大學本身水平都好有限"},{"pid":"a8746bbbd02c81391a70f36d354cc1bb3f5b05e0","tid":984542,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco